ansfer from state ownership to private ownership. <#/>Advocates of privatisation have put forward several reasons for the same. <#/>Indeed the most forceful and persuasive case for privatisation of parastatals was spelt out by the working party on governm
ent expenditure. <#/>In the report, it was argued that the government had intervened excessively in the economy. <#/>The report stated: 
