\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \lang2057 {<#/>From time immemorial forests have provided people with fuelwood for energy purposes in the domestic setting as well as wood for building houses. <X_>}{\v <#/>Women h
