n, due to oppressive patriarchal culture, which underlines women's experience. <#/>Due to the non-recognition of women's experiences and over-emphasis on male experiences, there is further environmental deterioration. <#/>That women do interact with the e
n
vironment in their daily activities cannot be denied, hence the need to carefully consider their needs and experiences. <#/>Solutions to environmental deterioration therefore need to consider these, and, from a feminist perspective, as argued by eco-femin
